  <!-- Home Page End -->
  <!-- Understanding Emotional -->
  <section>
    <h2
      class="md:hidden px-4 pt-[50px] text-[38px] leading-[38px] font-normal! md:font-medium"
    >
      Understanding Emotional Regulation:<span style="color: var(--blueGray)"
        >The Oxytocin Pathway to Clarity, Performance & Inner Balance</span
      >
    </h2>
    <div class="understanding-emotional max-w-[1450px]">
      <div class="w-1/2">
        <h2
          class="hidden md:block md:text-[50px] md:leading-[52px] font-medium!"
        >
          Understanding Emotional Regulation:<span
            style="color: var(--blueGray)"
            >The Oxytocin Pathway to Clarity, Performance & Inner Balance</span
          >
        </h2>
        <p
          style="font-size: 19px; text-transform: uppercase; inline-block mt-[15px]"
        >
          Regulate Emotions. Boost Focus. Elevate Mental Performance.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-[15px]">
          Emotion can shape how we think, decide, and perform. At the center of
          this process is oxytocin, a naturally occurring neurochemical that
          promotes trust, emotional balance, and stress relief. When triggered,
          either naturally or through VR and AI-enhanced immersive technology,
          oxytocin helps shift the brain from a stress response into a state of
          clarity and cognitive readiness. It enhances focus, strengthens
          working memory, and improves decision-making under pressure.<br /><br
          />
          <span style="font-weight: 600;color: var(--darkBlueGray);"
            >Repeated thoughts and imagery strengthen the pathways that guide
            behavior and choices, reinforcing this process over time.</span
